               <p>1377. <persName id="def1-1377-18430403" type="defendantName">
                     <interp inst="def1-1377-18430403" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     <interp inst="def1-1377-18430403" type="age" value="27"></interp>
                     <interp inst="def1-1377-18430403" type="surname" value="MOORE"></interp>
                     <interp inst="def1-1377-18430403" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>
                     <hi rend="largeCaps">JAMES MOORE</hi>
                  </persName>, was indicted<rs id="t18430403-1377-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18430403-1377-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18430403-1377-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="shoplifting"></interp> for stealing, on the <rs id="t18430403-cd-238" type="crimeDate">
                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18430403-1377-offence-1 t18430403-cd-238"></join>19th of March</rs>, I dead fowl, value 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18430403-name-1447" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18430403-name-1447" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430403-name-1447" type="surname" value="NICHOLSON"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430403-name-1447" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430403-name-1447" type="occupation" value="poulterer"></interp>
                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t18430403-1377-offence-1 t18430403-name-1447"></join>James Nicholson</persName>.</rs>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18430403-name-1448" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18430403-name-1448" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430403-name-1448" type="surname" value="WHITE"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430403-name-1448" type="given" value="GEORGE WILLIAM"></interp>GEORGE WILLIAM WHITE</persName>
                  </hi>. I am shopman to James Nicholson, he is a poulterer at Woolwich. The prisoner and another party came in while I</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="184304030193"></xptr>
               <p>was shutting up the shop about two o'clock on Sunday morning, the 19th of March—I served the other person with steaks and sausages—I did not like the prisoner's movements, and when the other had given me a shilling in pay<lb></lb>ment, I went round the counter, and missed a fowl—I saw the head of it under the prisoner's jacket, and after I had given change I went after them—I brought the prisoner back, and charged him with it—he said he did not know anything about it—I called the policeman, went with him, and found the fowl at Mr. Moss's door, which the prisoner had passed just before I took him.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner. Q.</hi> Was I not at the door of your shop when you accused me? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> No, I brought you back from where you had got to—you had a piece of timber in your hand, not under your arm.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">JURY</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> Are you quite satisfied that you saw him with the fowl under his arm going out? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> Quite—the door is narrow, and you are obliged to turn rather sideways to get out—it was not wood that he had under his arm, the wood was in his hand.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18430403-name-1449" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18430403-name-1449" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430403-name-1449" type="surname" value="HOLLOWAY"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430403-name-1449" type="given" value="JOSEPH"></interp>JOSEPH HOLLOWAY</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable R</hi> 137.) I was called, and found the prisoner in Mr. Nicholson's shop—I afterwards went and found the fowl at the step of the next house—the witness identified it—the prisoner first said he knew nothing about it, but when Mr. Nicholson was called, he said he did it for a <hi rend="italic">lark</hi>, and when he was taken to the station-house, he said it was his own.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner. Q.</hi> Do you say that I said I took it for a <hi rend="italic">lark? A.</hi> Yes, you had a stick of wood in your hand—I did not say I would <hi rend="italic">help you up</hi>—I said you had better be careful not to say anything to criminate yourself.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> The man and I went into the shop; the witness was serving him; I came to the door to go out; I did not go two steps from the door, and was returning again, when he came and accused me of taking a fowl; I said I knew nothing about it; I was not going to run away; if I had taken it it is not likely I would have returned.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <rs id="t18430403-1377-verdict-1" type="verdictDescription">
                        <interp inst="t18430403-1377-verdict-1" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430403-1377-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>. Aged 27.—<hi rend="italic">
                     <rs id="t18430403-1377-punishment-255" type="punishmentDescription">
                        <interp inst="t18430403-1377-punishment-255" type="punishmentCategory" value="imprison"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430403-1377-punishment-255" type="punishmentSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>
                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-1377-18430403 t18430403-1377-punishment-255"></join>Confined One Month</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Common Sergeant.</hi>
